    public final class RouteBundleExtras
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    An extra container contains extras and interceptors

    extras: the extra bundle data set by IBaseRoute.addExtras(Bundle) interceptors: the extra RouteInterceptor set by IBaseRoute.addInterceptor(RouteInterceptor)

    另请参阅:
    IBaseRoute
